Interface IQuaternion

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Quaternion

    public interface IQuaternion
    Provides read-only access to a Quaternion.

      • toAngles

        Vector3 toAngles(Vector3 result)
        Computes the angles to pass to Quaternion.fromAngles(pythagoras.f.Vector3) to reproduce this rotation, placing them in the provided vector. This uses the factorization method described in David Eberly's Euler Angle Formulas.
        Returns:
        a reference to the result vector, for chaining.

      • toAngles

        Vector3 toAngles()
        Computes and returns the angles to pass to Quaternion.fromAngles(pythagoras.f.Vector3) to reproduce this rotation.
        Returns:
        a new vector containing the resulting angles.
